## Overview
Buttons allow users to take actions with a single tap.

## Variants
| Variant | Usage | Visual |
|---------|-------|--------|
| Primary | Main actions | Filled, brand color |
| Secondary | Alternative actions | Outlined |
| Ghost | Tertiary actions | No border/background |
| Danger | Destructive actions | Red filled |

## States
- Default
- Hover
- Active/Pressed
- Focus
- Disabled
- Loading

